  "texts": [
    "Blood samples were collected at baseline and at the end of the study.",
    "On the second visit, the participants were submitted to a clinical evaluation of resting heart rate, blood pressure, medical history, body composition, aerobic capacity, muscle strength, PA and SB, QoL, anxiety and depression tests, performed by a physiologist at the laboratory of the University of Évora.",
    "Participants were asked to bring any medications that they were taking to the assessments.",
    "Initially, each participant completed a standardized questionnaire including demographic data, medical history, medication use, family history of CVD, and smoking status.",
    "They also completed the patient-reported QoL questionnaire and the Hospital Anxiety and Depression Scale (HADS)."
